metadata.name: MUTANT APE #1
metadata.description:
Zombie King BAYC #8944, who has infected countless monkeys, is planning to invade the planet klaytn using mutant monkeys. 
 In a secret ancient cave, he learns how to make the legendary solar carriage written in 'mystic documents' that transcends time and space. 
        
        Legendary 1
        If you collect 12 signs of zodiac
        You can ride the solar carriage and go out into space
        The spaceship departs only when 12 apes are on board
        You will get powerful abilities with fire inside the spaceship
        The 12 riders can go anywhere in Klaytn and Ethereum
        
        Legendary 2
        Spaceships transcend time and space.
        It will definitely be powerful
        when you are on the Ethereum planet.
        You will also have time to heal while you are on the ship.
        new special features of the ship are a hidden legend
